{"tid":1825284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[下架韓國瑜] 選後民調：高雄市過半民眾支持罷免韓國瑜","createTime":"2020-01-15T06:49:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T03:21:38.000Z","uid":52658,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"484828c2b7a0a34ddc1ce9235b42c0deddf71d5f","tid":1825284,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:49:34.000Z","msg":"2020大選落幕，國民黨在總統、區域立委雙雙落敗，而高雄市長韓國瑜回到高雄市還要面對we care高雄的罷免問題，而民調顯示，竟有過半民眾支持韓國瑜的罷免案！<br />\n<br />\n根據TVBS的最新民調指出，高雄市民有53%同意罷免，而不支持罷免的人佔32%；而調查中有8%表示不會去投票，而有7%的人不表示意見。<br />\n<br />\n民調結果顯示，韓國瑜在選後面對憤怒的市民，恐怕還需要更大的努力，而距離罷免還有四個多月，這段時間韓市長是否能挽回高雄市民的信任，是外界共同關注的焦點。"},{"pid":"83fedc2c315a69432767e0999c9d722abb10bff2","tid":1825284,"uid":50196,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.vjmedia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/23/200286/78f59195407c4677d612ec33b819864a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F23%2F200286%2F78f59195407c4677d612ec33b819864a.jpg&h=9fec45fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0d6a5a936bf31da8f3117598d18f0fbd77f5e57","tid":1825284,"uid":146737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T06:50:55.000Z","msg":"【第廿貳期牆紙】 為良知發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824896/page/1</a><br />\nFB : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F852wallpaper%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=41c5d01f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/852wallpaper/</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=85b7d360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\